snippet.title: Regular Home Renovation Simulator — Trailer
snippet.description:
Regular Home Renovation Simulator - a house fixing game, filled with mysteries that await the brave souls that dare play it. Repair houses, broken-down churches and desolate basements. Scrape the stains. The dirt. And don’t forget the blood. Remove viscera and entrails. Become the One That Wakes The Mother.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2601530
